hopobject.body: Recorded Delivery cefadroxil rxlist The Focus 1.0-litre EcoBoost will emit a tax-friendly 99 g/km and will do almost 70 mpg thanks to a combination of using the company's brilliant and multi-award winning 1.0 litre engine. It has been specially calibrated to develop 100PS as well as using low rolling resistance tyres which need less power to push them over the road, unique aerodynamics with underbody panels to smooth the airflow and reduce power-sapping drag and the radiator grille which closes at speed to again reduce drag and revised gearing.
